                    <p>A quantidade total de quilogramas de ingredientes utilizados na receita é</p>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <ol type="A">
                            <li><input type="radio" name="q6" value="A" maxlength="1"> 0,335 kg.</li>
                            <li><input type="radio" name="q6" value="B" maxlength="1"> 1,185 kg.</li>
                            <li><input type="radio" name="q6" value="C" maxlength="1"> 335 kg.</li>
                            <li><input type="radio" name="q6" value="D" maxlength="1"> 1185 kg.</li>
